sections.heading: abatement project; firm; license required
sections.text: Except as otherwise provided in the Residential Lead-Based Paint Professions Practice Act, a firm shall not engage in an abatement project unless the firm holds a license for that purpose.SourceLaws 1994, LB 1210, ยง 168;Laws 1999, LB 863, ยง 43;Laws 2007, LB4
